                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <ul class="footer-other-links clearfix">
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>How much will it cost?</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>Frequently asked questions </a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>Customer tesimonials</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>Recent works </a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>Help &amp; Support Center</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#"><em class="fas fa-check-circle"></em>Get a free quote </a></li>
